name: 5-minuterecipes
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: five minute recipes
des:
With Five minute recipes, you can choose among thousands of recipes the perfect meal for your breakfast, brunch, dinner and lunch, original sandwiches to prepare for work, healthy and tasty snacks and scrumptious desserts to impress your guests with a minimal effort.

Guided by your personal voice assistant, you can apply filters to the selection, listen to alternatives until you find what really pamper your taste-buds!

Follow the preparation step by step, ask for alternative ingredients, stop and pause any time to complete the recipe at your pace.

You'll be surprised by your culinary skills!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
